Output demos/7_key_change.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"

Type "cargo run -- demos/7_key_change.json"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type ":7"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "n"
Sleep 1s
Type "A"
Type "key: Bb"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "n"
Sleep 1s
Type "n"
Sleep 500ms
Type "A"
Backspace 7
Type "key: B"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type ":wq"
Enter
